PN,43101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FSouth West Water has been fined #1.9
OL,7,Fmillion after admitting supplying
OL,8,Fwater that was unfit for human
OL,9,Fconsumption in South Devon.
OL,11,F537 people were left unwell and 10
OL,12,Fwere hospitalised after the water
OL,13,Fsupply was contaminated with the
OL,14,Fparasite cryptosporidium in Brixham in
OL,15,FMay 2024.
OL,17,FAround 16,000 homes and businesses in
OL,18,FBrixham, Kingswear and Paignton - a
OL,19,Fpopulation of almost 39,000 - were
OL,20,Ftold to boil their water and the
OL,21,Fnotice was not lifted until July 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FAt Exeter Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FTuesday, District Judge Stuart Smith
OL,8,Fsaid South West Water was guilty of a
OL,9,F'serious failure' to protect the
OL,10,Fpublic and a 'systemic failure of
OL,11,Fgovernance within the organisation'
OL,12,Fwhich left a 'deep and lasting harm'.
OL,14,F"This was a major public health
OL,15,Fincident," he said.
OL,17,F"Public services were disrupted,
OL,18,Fconfidence in the region's drinking
OL,19,Fwater was seriously undermined. The
OL,20,Fcompany did not take reasonable steps
OL,21,Fto avoid the supply of unfit water."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FJoseph Millington, representing the
OL,7,FDrinking Water Inspectorate (DWI),
OL,8,Fsaid the crisis 'undermined trust and
OL,9,Fconfidence' in the water supply and
OL,10,Fhad a 'serious adverse effect' on the
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"The parasite entered the water supply
OL,14,Fthrough a damaged air valve in a water
OL,15,Fpipe on farmland used for cattle," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"The damaged air valve was covered in
OL,19,Fmud, with water pooling across the
OL,20,Fsurface of the field and found to be
OL,21,Fleaking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"A soil sample next to that valve
OL,7,Ftested positive for cryptosporidium.
OL,9,F"The defendant failed to inspect that
OL,10,Fair valve adequately, and the
OL,11,Fdefendant also failed to inspect the
OL,12,Ffarm which was characterised as a high-
OL,13,Frisk site."
OL,15,FThe court heard that people had been
OL,16,Ffalling ill in Brixham for several
OL,17,Fdays before the parasite was
OL,18,Fdiscovered, and the public were told
OL,19,Fto 'continue using the water supply as
OL,20,Fnormal'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FSouth West Water issued an 'unreserved
OL,7,Fapology' for the incident and said it
OL,8,Fwished to express its 'genuine remorse
OL,9,Fin relation to this incident.'
OL,11,FThe company agreed to pay the #75,000
OL,12,Fcost of the prosecution.
OL,14,F'It was almost unbearable'
OL,16,FJohn Thackray owns a garage in
OL,17,FBrixham. He was among the first people
OL,18,Fto become unwell after drinking tap
OL,19,Fwater in May 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"I was becoming very feverish, very
OL,7,Fachy all over, my joints and muscles.
OL,8,FVery very tired.
OL,10,F"Along with that was the extreme,
OL,11,Fsickness and diarrhoea. I couldn't
OL,12,Feven keep a sip of water down, the
OL,13,Fminute anything hit me inside, I was
OL,14,Fsuffering with extreme diarrhoea.
OL,16,F"That then progressed into blood loss,
OL,17,Fto the point where I was having to
OL,18,Fmake trips to the hospital to be
OL,19,Fmonitored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"I didn't realise at the time how bad
OL,7,Fmy illness was to become. It got to
OL,8,Fthe point where it was almost
OL,9,Funbearable."
OL,11,FJohn has recently experienced what he
OL,12,Fdescribes as another 'flare-up', which
OL,13,Fhe believes is linked to the original
OL,14,Fbout of Cryptosporidiosis.
OL,16,F"Exactly the same symptoms as before,
OL,17,Fa mirror image of two years ago," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,F"My tummy has never been the same
OL,21,Fsince I've had it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"It may never leave. From the people
OL,7,Fthat I've spoken to, the doctors, and
OL,8,Fthe research I've done as well,
OL,9,FCryptosporidium can live in the body
OL,10,Fforever and it may just be something I
OL,11,Fhave to live with. So it's frightening.
OL,13,F"I was told it was perfectly safe to
OL,14,Fdrink, there's nothing wrong with it,
OL,15,Fand then before you know it there were
OL,16,Fwater stations dotted around Brixham.
OL,17,FSo clearly, they lied.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"There's no amount of money that will
OL,7,Fmake it okay, especially for those
OL,8,Fthat are still suffering and those
OL,9,Fthat are having to live with damaged
OL,10,Fhealth as a direct result of drinking
OL,11,Fthe infected water."
OL,13,FThe court heard that back in 2020, the
OL,14,FDWI told South West Water it needed to
OL,15,Fregularly inspect air valves in its
OL,16,Fnetwork, which can pose a risk to
OL,17,Fwater quality due to agricultural
OL,18,Factivities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FMr Millington said the company wrote a
OL,7,Fnew policy, but it was never
OL,8,Fimplemented and air valves were not
OL,9,Finspected.
OL,11,F"The farm itself had never been
OL,12,Finspected, despite presenting a
OL,13,Fsignificant risk," he said.
OL,15,F'They could have stopped this'
OL,17,FJo Byrne, who owns a Post Office in
OL,18,FKingswear, also became unwell at the
OL,19,Ftime of the outbreak and still has
OL,20,Fsymptoms today.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"Before it became big news, there was
OL,7,Fa whole neighbourhood that was sick,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,F"They kept telling the water company
OL,11,F'Everybody in this neighbourhood is
OL,12,Fsick, some of us are going to the
OL,13,Fhospital, it must be the water, can
OL,14,Fyou check it?'
OL,16,F"They said we could keep drinking the
OL,17,Fwater, but they were checking the main
OL,18,Fplant, not Hillhead where it was
OL,19,Fcoming from.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"They could have stopped this, they
OL,7,Fcould have saved a whole load of
OL,8,Fpeople from getting sick, but they
OL,9,Fdidn't want to admit they had a
OL,10,Fproblem.
OL,12,F"It was a terrible summer, horrific. I
OL,13,Fwas really sick, I lost a lot of
OL,14,Fweight really quick.
OL,16,F"I have irritable bowel syndrome now
OL,17,Fbecause of it. I have flare-ups
OL,18,Fsometimes that feel like the first
OL,19,Ftime I got sick.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"I don't drink tap water ever anymore,
OL,7,FI use bottled water, I'll brush my
OL,8,Fteeth and shower but I will not drink
OL,9,Fit. I don't trust it. I mean, how can
OL,10,Fyou?"
OL,12,F'There should be custodial sentences'
OL,14,FJen Watts' 10-year-old son was
OL,15,Fhospitalised and later developed
OL,16,FAvoidant Restrictive Food Intake
OL,17,FDisorder.
OL,19,FThe impact has been so severe that he
OL,20,Fwill still not allow people in their
OL,21,Fhome.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"Like all mums, you just want your
OL,7,Fchild to be healthy and happy," Jen
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"As a result of what happened, he is
OL,11,Fgoing to need a lot more support. I
OL,12,Fwill do whatever I can do to make sure
OL,13,Fhe gets that.
OL,15,F"While this sentencing and significant
OL,16,Ffine sends a very clear message that
OL,17,Fit's not acceptable for these water
OL,18,Fcompanies to allow this sort of thing
OL,19,Fto happen, I think there really should
OL,20,Fbe custodial sentences as a result of
OL,21,Fthis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"I don't think the punishment is
OL,7,Fstrong enough, given the severity and
OL,8,Fthe impact it's had on people, on
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,F"It's caused life-changing,
OL,12,Fdevastating problems. We've been
OL,13,Fliving with this now for two years and
OL,14,Fit's not going away."
OL,16,FCaroline Voaden, MP for South Devon
OL,17,Fsaid: "It is disappointing after this
OL,18,Flengthy saga to see South West Water
OL,19,Fescape with such a small fine.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"The primary purpose of a water
OL,7,Fcompany is to supply clean drinkable
OL,8,Fwater to its customers. On that count,
OL,9,FSWW clearly failed.
OL,11,F"I am sure many in Brixham will feel
OL,12,Fthe punishment dished out to SWW does
OL,13,Fnot reflect the seriousness of the
OL,14,Fcontamination or the effects it had on
OL,15,Fpublic health and the local economy.
OL,17,F"Nobody should be making a profit from
OL,18,Fwater and until the government accepts
OL,19,Fthis, we will never see the scale of
OL,20,Freform needed to turn the industry
OL,21,Faround."
OL,26,@}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F'Lives turned upside down'
OL,8,FPersonal injury lawyer Jatinder Paul,
OL,9,Ffrom Irwin Mitchell Solicitors, is
OL,10,Frepresenting a group of those most
OL,11,Fseriously impacted by the parasite who
OL,12,Fare pursuing civil claims against
OL,13,FSouth West Water.
OL,15,F"These are the more complicated cases
OL,16,Fwhere there are considerable residual
OL,17,Fsymptoms as a result of the initial
OL,18,Fillnesses that our clients have
OL,19,Fsuffered," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"Some of them have had their lives
OL,7,Fturned upside down. It's important to
OL,8,Fremember that this is not just a few
OL,9,Fweeks of diarrhoea and vomiting. Some
OL,10,Fof these people have been left with
OL,11,Flife changing complications.
OL,13,F"Our sincere hope is that South West
OL,14,FWater have have learnt from this
OL,15,Fmistake.
OL,17,F"If this happens again, we would
OL,18,Fexpect them to hold their hands up
OL,19,Fmuch sooner and admit that something's
OL,20,Fgone wrong so that their customers can
OL,21,Fbe warned as quickly as possible."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FIn total the outbreak cost South West
OL,7,FWater #16.3 million in compensation it
OL,8,Fhad to pay to affected customers.
OL,10,FThe company then pledged a #1.2
OL,11,Fmillion fund to try and help tourism
OL,12,Frecover over the three years,
OL,13,Ffollowing the reputational damage
OL,14,Fcaused by the outbreak.
OL,16,FOver the eight weeks, more than 1,000
OL,17,FSouth West Water network technicians,
OL,18,Fengineers, water quality scientists
OL,19,Fand contractors worked on rotation 24
OL,20,Fhours-a-day to try and resolve the
OL,21,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FOver 34km of water pipes needed to be
OL,7,Fflushed 27 times at high velocity to
OL,8,Fclean network pipes and remove
OL,9,Fcryptosporidium. They also carried out
OL,10,F17 phases of ice-pigging and swabbing
OL,11,F` a more aggressive cleaning approach.
OL,13,F'Something wasn't right here'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43121
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FDr Beth Smout, regional deputy
OL,7,Fdirector of the UK Health Security
OL,8,FAgency, said: "This was a very
OL,9,Fsignificant situation. Outbreaks of
OL,10,FCryprosporidium linked to drinking
OL,11,Fwater are thankfully very rare, they
OL,12,Fdo not happen commonly. They tend to
OL,13,Fcome from places like petting farms,
OL,14,For from people wild swimming in rivers
OL,15,Fand things like that.
OL,17,F"An outbreak linked to drinking water
OL,18,Fis very unusual, and this was a very
OL,19,Fsignificant outbreak in terms of its
OL,20,Fscale.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G21/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43122
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"This really stressed the importance
OL,7,Fof having early warning systems in
OL,8,Fplace. GPs in the local area calling
OL,9,Fus to say they were receiving an
OL,10,Funusually high number of reports of
OL,11,Fpeople with diarrhoea and vomiting;
OL,12,Fand members of the public reporting
OL,13,Ftheir experiences on social media,
OL,14,Fthose all came together to give us
OL,15,Fthat early warning that something
OL,16,Fwasn't right, something was different
OL,17,Fhere and we needed to take further
OL,18,Faction."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G22/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43123
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FDominic Kay KC, representing South
OL,7,FWest Water in court, said: "The
OL,8,Fcompany issues an unreserved apology,
OL,9,Fand wishes to record publicly its
OL,10,Fgenuine remorse in relation to this
OL,11,Fincident."
OL,13,FCllr Julian Brazil, Liberal Democrat
OL,14,Fleader of Devon County Council, said:
OL,15,F"We need to have some proper, strong
OL,16,Flegislation from government, and
OL,17,Fgovernment needs to get a bit of
OL,18,Fpolitical courage. We will hear the
OL,19,Fusual 'lessons learned' and 'we are
OL,20,Fsincerely sorry', and nothing will
OL,21,Fhappen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G23/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43124
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"We need to ensure that the executives
OL,7,Fare held accountable. The bigger
OL,8,Fpicture is that these water companies
OL,9,Fare not being held to account. They're
OL,10,Fcontinuing as they are. There's still
OL,11,Fobscene executive pay. They're more
OL,12,Finterested in share price and
OL,13,Fdividends than they are in actually
OL,14,Fdoing their job."
OL,16,FWe need to rebuild trust - South West
OL,17,FWater
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G24/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43125
SC,0025
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FDavid Harris, Managing Director Water
OL,7,FServices, South West Water said: "We
OL,8,Fhave co-operated fully with the
OL,9,FDrinking Water Inspectorate throughout
OL,10,Fits investigations and through the end
OL,11,Fof the legal process today.
OL,13,F"We apologise again to our customers
OL,14,Fwho were impacted and have always
OL,15,Ftaken full responsibility for the
OL,16,Fwater that was supplied.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G25/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43126
SC,0026
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"Hundreds of our skilled colleagues
OL,7,Fworked tirelessly to fix the issues
OL,8,Ffaced during the incident. We will
OL,9,Fcontinue to work every day to rebuild
OL,10,Ftrust and our relationships with the
OL,11,Fcommunities who were impacted by this
OL,12,Fextremely rare event in 2024.
OL,14,F"That started during the incident
OL,15,Fitself where the prosecution
OL,16,Facknowledged today in court that South
OL,17,FWest Water went above and beyond with
OL,18,Frespect to the provision of bottled
OL,19,Fwater and more generally made no
OL,20,Fcriticism of our incident response.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G26/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43127
SC,0027
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"We have also developed smart air
OL,7,Fvalves - an industry leading step up -
OL,8,Fand changed our processes to ensure
OL,9,Fearlier precautionary boil water
OL,10,Fnotices can be issued where necessary."
OL,12,FKeith Haslett, Chief Executive
OL,13,FOfficer, Pennon Group added: While I
OL,14,Fhave only been CEO of this business
OL,15,Ffor a few weeks, it is very clear that
OL,16,Fwe must learn lessons from this
OL,17,Fincident and work hard to rebuild
OL,18,Ftrust with the customers and
OL,19,Fcommunities we serve, both in Brixham
OL,20,Fand beyond.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G27/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43128
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,F"I am already focussed on driving
OL,7,Fimprovement in the way we operate, how
OL,8,Fwe communicate and support our
OL,9,Fcustomers during operational
OL,10,Fincidents, and driving a step change
OL,11,Fin our performance for our customers
OL,12,Fand the environment."
OL,14,FWhat is cryptosporidium?
OL,16,FCryptosporidium is a microscopic
OL,17,Fparasite that causes infections
OL,18,Faffecting both people and farm animals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G28/29
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43129
SC,0029
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1780419953
OL,3,CSouth West Water fined #1.9m for
OL,4,CBrixham infected water scandal
OL,6,FIt can be found in rivers, untreated
OL,7,Fdrinking water and occasionally in
OL,8,Fswimming pools throughout the UK.
OL,10,FYou can contract cryptosporidiosis
OL,11,F(the infection caused by
OL,12,FCryptosporidium) directly from another
OL,13,Fperson or animal by coming into
OL,14,Fcontact with faeces and then touching
OL,15,Fyour mouth without thorough
OL,16,Fhandwashing.
OL,18,FThe main symptoms of infection include:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G29/29
